<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb524ec6c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s274i–3"><num value="274i–3">§ 274i–3.</num><heading> Medals not treated as valuable consideration</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">A medal under this part shall not be treated as valuable consideration for purposes of <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s274e/a">section 274e(a) of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb524ec6d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/110/413/s5">Pub. L. 110–413, § 5</ref>, <date date="2008-10-14">Oct. 14, 2008</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/122/4340">122 Stat. 4340</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
